/* DESIRED: Check the boxes if they're selected. */ /* Run an event handler that refreshes the passage when an option changes. */ <<run checkboxHandler("nsfw1"); checkboxHandler("nsfw2"); checkboxHandler("nsfw3"); checkboxHandler("nsfw"); function checkboxHandler(content) { let warn_content = "input#checkbox--warn-" + content; $(warn_content).on("click", function() { if (document.querySelector(warn_content).checked) { /* Ensure the content isn't already in the array. */ if (!variables().ft_warning.includes(content)) { variables().ft_warning.push(content); } } else {
